#: ../../mail.rst:185
msgid ""
"For security reasons, all protocols require STARTTLS encryption by default."
"  The :guilabel:`Allow unencrypted connections`, disables this important "
"requirement, and allows passing clear-text passwords and mail contents on "
"the network."
